title: #2: CSI: Carol Danvers
body:
It’s episode two! Mar-Vell gets more superhero-y! Stuff happens to Una! General craziness! Thor: Ragnarok jokes! Carol’s bloodhound instincts! Zo, the Giant Magical Talking Monument! Mar-Vell encounters Cuba and Iron Man! Anthony Stark’s portfolio! Old School Black Widow! Hasselhoff Nick Fury! Do you notice a lack of mentions of Carol in this description? There’s a reason for that! Join us for a discussion of Captain Marvel #10 – 14.


Check out this episode!
